        <p class="text-base md:text-[22px] lg:max-w-[85%] text-center lg:text-left tracking-tight font-jost text-text-gray leading-[33px]">We understand that a clean environment reflects your business standards. That's why we approach every project with meticulous attention to detail and a commitment to exceeding expectations.</p>
      </div>
      <img src="/about1.png" alt="FCM cleaning team at work">
    </div>
  </section>

