        <p class="text-base md:text-[22px] lg:max-w-[95%] text-center lg:text-left tracking-tight font-jost text-text-gray leading-[33px]">We invest in our team through ongoing training and provide them with professional-grade equipment and environmentally-friendly cleaning products. This combination allows us to deliver superior cleaning services that meet the highest industry standards.</p>
